HR Management System – Full Stack Project

A complete Human Resources Management System built using ASP.NET Core Web API for the backend and Angular for the frontend.
The system manages employees, attendance, roles & permissions, organization settings, commissions, deductions, and weekly off days.

Table of Contents

Overview

Features

Technologies Used

Backend (ASP.NET Core Web API)

Frontend (Angular)


This project provides a structured HR system that supports:

Role management (CRUD + permissions)

Attendance & absence tracking

Organization settings management

Commission & deduction calculation (hour-based or amount-based)

Weekly off day selection (max 2 days)

Employee management

Authentication & Authorization using ASP.NET Identity


Features
 Backend Features

Authentication using JWT

Role creation, update, and deletion

Updating role names with permission re-mapping

Managing organization settings

Weekly off-day logic with validation

Repository + Service layer

DTOs and clean API responses

 Frontend Features (Angular)

Fully working UI for all modules

Role update page with routing state

Weekly off-day checkboxes (max 2)

Dynamic forms for commission/deduction

Toastr notifications

Clean component structure

API integration with interceptors


